  "prompt": "What are best computer games?",
  "response": "Determining the \"best\" computer games can be quite subjective, as it often depends on personal preferences, including genre, gameplay style, storytelling, graphics, and more. However, some games have been widely acclaimed by critics and players alike. As of recent years, here are a few titles often mentioned among the best computer games:\n\n1. **The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt** - Known for its rich story, deep characters, and expansive open world, this RPG is highly praised for immersing players in a vividly detailed fantasy universe.\n\n2. **Red Dead Redemption 2** - This open-world adventure game is celebrated for its stunning graphics, engaging narrative, and the realism of its frontier world.\n\n3. **Half-Life: Alyx** - A VR-exclusive game that pushes the boundaries of virtual reality, it's hailed for its immersive experience and high-quality narrative.\n\n4. **Civilization VI** - Part of the long-running strategy series, it is praised for its depth, accessibility, and replayability.\n\n5. **Hades** - An action roguelike known for its fast-paced gameplay and unique approach to storytelling, as well as its vibrant art style.\n\n6. **Minecraft** - A sandbox game with a massive following, known for its limitless creativity and wide-ranging community of players.\n\n7. **Cyberpunk 2077** - Despite a rocky launch, this game has been praised for its complex narrative, intricate world-building, and role-playing depth.\n\n8. **Dark Souls III** - Known for its challenging gameplay and atmospheric environments, it's a beloved title in the action RPG genre.\n\n9. **Dota 2** and **League of Legends** - Popular in the MOBA (Multiplayer Online Battle Arena) genre, both games have massive eSports scenes and dedicated player bases.\n\n10. **Valorant** - A tactical shooter that combines precise gunplay with character abilities, it quickly became popular in the competitive gaming scene.\n\nThese selections represent a mix of genres and styles, each with its own distinct appeal. It's worth exploring reviews and gameplay footage to find which of these might align best with your gaming preferences.",
